1. *Kolači* su mi omiljena poslastica. (Cakes are my favorite dessert.)
2. Molim te, donesi mi *kolač* iz pekare. (Please bring me a cake from the bakery.)
3. Imamo *kolačić* za svakog gosta. (We have a cookie for every guest.)
4. *Kolačiće* sam pekla sinoć. (I baked cookies last night.)
5. Sutra ću praviti *kolače* za rođendansku proslavu. (Tomorrow I will make cakes for the birthday party.)
6. Njena majka je vrlo dobra u pravljenju *kolača*. (Her mother is very good at making cakes.)
7. Oni su kupili veliku *kolačarsku* peć. (They bought a large cake baking oven.)
8. Na tržištu ima mnogo različitih vrsta *kolača*. (There are many different types of cakes on the market.)
9. *Kolačići* su idealni za posluživanje s čajem ili kavom. (Cookies are ideal to serve with tea or coffee.)
10. Jela je *kolač* s velikim užitkom. (She enjoyed the cake very much.)